<TextFlow columnCount="inherit" columnGap="inherit" columnWidth="inherit" lineBreak="inherit" paddingBottom="inherit" paddingLeft="inherit" paddingRight="inherit" paddingTop="inherit" paragraphSpaceBefore="0" verticalAlign="inherit" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008"><p textIndent="39"><span fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24">这是一款基于as3的在线文档编辑器，使用flash builder4制作，主要使用textlayoutAPI,基本实现了TLF的所有功能。当然，由于TLF的限制，很多</span><span fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41">功能无法实现，如高级图文混排，表格等。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41">以下是本编辑器的主要功能展示。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41">文本功能：</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41">1、字体：</span><span fontFamily="宋体" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41">这是宋体字,</span><span color="#ff0000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41">这是红色字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41">,</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.4705882352941177">这是透明度50%黑色字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">，</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="48" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">这是48号字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">，</span><span backgroundColor="#0000ff" color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">这是背景蓝色字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">，</span><span backgroundAlpha="0.4705882352941177" backgroundColor="#0000ff" color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">这是背景透明度50%字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="41" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">，</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="bold" lineHeight="41" lineThrough="true" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textDecoration="underline">这是加粗斜体带下划线删</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="bold" lineThrough="true" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textDecoration="underline">除线字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">，</span><span baselineShift="superscript" color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">这是上标字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">，</span><span baselineShift="subscript" color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">这是下标字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902">，</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="rotate270">这是旋转指定角度文字</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">。</span></p><p textIndent="38"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="43" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">2、行：编辑</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" lineHeight="60" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">器支持行高度调整</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">，以实现行距功能，让显示更美观。文本行高度的调整完全可通过调整基线参数来解决，有兴趣的可试验一下，这里不再赘述。</span></p><p textIndent="38"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">3、字间距：可以任意调整选定区域的字符左右间距：</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto" trackingLeft="30">这是字符左间隙为30</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">，</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto" trackingRight="30">这是字符右间距为50</span><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">。</span></p><p textIndent="38"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">4、编辑：提供了基本剪切、粘贴、删除操作，撤销、重做造作只是基于TFL的堆栈，大部分操作可以撤销，但不是全部。</span></p><p textIndent="38"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">5、插入图片：目前可以插入网络其他地址的图片，因为是信息流载入，所以不存在沙箱问题。当然，保存的也只是图片信息，而不是将图片保存到服务器。后续版本将加入上传图片到服务器并现实的功能。图片高度、宽度可以设置成范围内数字，0表示宽度、高度自动判断。这是插入图片的例子：</span><img color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto" height="auto" width="auto" source="http://www.baidu.com/img/baidu_logo.gif"/><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">插入链接：要先选定一段文本，此功能将文本转为超链接。但在编辑状态下，链接无法响应鼠标的点击事件。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">插入文本：这功能比较鸡肋，相当于粘贴。由于TLY支持常用快捷键，直接ctrl+v即可。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">6、段落：</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">首行缩进的单位是像素，因此，对于字体不同的行，缩进的值是不一样的，使用中须注意。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">横向对齐也是针对段的，同MS-office中的段落对齐方式没有本质差别。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">纵向对齐是针对整个编辑容器的，在分栏后，针对每个栏。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">段前距离、段后距离可控制段落与段落之间的距离。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto">7、视图：这些功能都是针对整个容易，而不是段落。特此说明。</span></p><p textIndent="39"><span color="#000000" fontFamily="仿宋" fontSize="24" textAlpha="0.9607843137254902" textRotation="auto"></span></p></TextFlow>